ActSpecial Economic Measures Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Special Economic Measures (Hamas Terrorist Attacks) Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the SPECIAL ECONOMIC MEASURES (HAMAS TERRORIST ATTACKS) REGULATIONS in order to add eleven (11) individuals and two (2) entities to the Schedule of the Regulations, prohibiting them from transacting business with individuals and businesses in Canada, and freezing their assets unless otherwise authorized by the Minister of the Foreign Affairs.
RegistrationRegistration: SOR/ 2024-0178 Publication Date: 2024-10-09
AttachmentsAttachment
